author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: When 'Естествена кожа' checkbox is clicked mixed results are shown instead of only products with fabric 'Естествена кожа'

author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: List element 'Обувки от 99.99лв' is partially outside of the drop-down menu

title: Hovering over categories 'H8S', 'Outlet', 'Нови' doesn't trigger a drop-down menu
author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: Drop-down menus aren't being triggered by hovering over the 'H8S', 'Outlet', 'Нови' categories

title: New password can be changed to a current password
author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: An error message isn't being displayed and the new password is successfully changed to the current one

author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: The quantity of the item in the wishlist is increased by one and no error message is displayed

author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: The quick order form only allows a single size option, 'one size'

title: Edit the color of an added to the cart item doesn't work as expected
author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: The page is reloaded, button 'Актуализирай количката' is replaced by 'Добави' button and it's not possible for the color to be edited

title: Sign up with an invalid surname successfully registers a user
author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: No error message appears on the screen and the registration is successfull

title: Sign up with an invalid first name successfully registers a user
author: Svetoslava Stoyanova
actual result: No error message appears on the screen and the registration is successfull
